        "review_xhfWWT": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "score": 5,
            "date": "10/01/2025",
            "title": "Roy Quintero",
            "intro": "<p>Awesome little bikes! (Got one for my 10 year old son & one for myself to ride with him). He Loves it! Thanks Yozma!!</p>",
            "comment_image": "shopify://shop_images/1759347104__1759347036301-img_8552__original.avif",
            "type": "text"
          }
        },
        "review_ciUkQc": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "score": 5,
            "date": "10/01/2025",
            "title": "Simon A",
            "intro": "<p>Very good bike for the price. Assembly was a bit tedious but overall the bike is soo much fun!</p>",
            "comment_image": "shopify://shop_images/1759353319__1759353309295-img_9946__original.avif",
            "type": "text"
          }
        },
        "review_MdArPw": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "score": 5,
            "date": "10/09/2025",
            "title": "Rksinc57",
            "intro": "<p>We received this bike 4 days ago for my grandson's birthday. It didn't take long to put together but out of the box the display unit was badly cracked and unreadable. We emailed Yozma and they responded within 1 day and are sending a replacement. That is great service! In the meantime, it has not stopped my grandson from riding and loving this dirt bike. He has already put 50 miles on it and loves it. We got him a nice helmet and gloves to keep him safe. I tried to keep him at speed level 2 but you know what a 13 year old boy will do..... He gets close to around 32 mph (68 inches tall). The build quality of the bike seems to be great (I am a mechanical engineer).<br/><br/></p>",
            "comment_image": "shopify://shop_images/1760034548__img_9021__original.avif",
            "type": "text"
          }
        },
        "review_z7BLNP": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "score": 5,
            "date": "10/07/2025",
            "title": "Josh Franc",
            "intro": "<p>I got mine today and its been great. Much more power than expected</p>",
            "comment_image": "shopify://shop_images/1759806197__1759806192331-1000003572__original.avif",
            "type": "text"
          }
        }
      },
